Text: Is this your usual retarded "everything but the match"?hours of pre match studio waffle,no football whatsoever then hours more studio waffle.If you love football DO NOT download from these people,they obviously know nothing about the game as their "extended highlights" of Real vs Barca contained NO highlights whatsoever,just an hour of live studio talk.Totally retarded.BEWARE.BEWARE.BEWARE.They may have pages and pages of good stuff but their football sucks like the biggest retard ever.I'd like to know why you,TvTeam upload everything except the game?
